:"https://api.github.com/users/mpkorstanje/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mpkorstanje/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mpkorstanje/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mpkorstanje/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}],"milestone":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/junit-team/junit-framework/milestones/66","html_url":"https://github.com/junit-team/junit-framework/milestone/66","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/junit-team/junit-framework/milestones/66/labels","id":8591660,"node_id":"MI_kwDOAbwRH84Agxks","number":66,"title":"5.9.2","description":"","creator":{"login":"marcphilipp","id":214207,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIxNDIwNw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/214207?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp","html_url":"https://github.com/marcphilipp","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"open_issues":0,"closed_issues":12,"state":"closed","created_at":"2022-10-28T10:22:13Z","updated_at":"2023-01-10T11:13:11Z","due_on":"2023-01-10T08:00:00Z","closed_at":"2023-01-10T11:13:11Z"},"comments":0,"created_at":"2022-09-24T13:18:05Z","updated_at":"2023-01-06T17:30:12Z","closed_at":"2022-10-15T12:44:16Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nUsing JUnit Jupiter 5.9.1 on Java 9+ with \r\n\r\n```properties\r\njunit.jupiter.execution.parallel.enabled=true\r\njunit.jupiter.execution.parallel.config.strategy=custom\r\njunit.jupiter.execution.parallel.config.custom.class=com.example.BadConfig\r\n```\r\n\r\n```java\r\npackage com.example;\r\n\r\nimport org.junit.platform.engine.ConfigurationParameters;\r\nimport org.junit.platform.engine.support.hierarchical.ParallelExecutionConfiguration;\r\nimport org.junit.platform.engine.support.hierarchical.ParallelExecutionConfigurationStrategy;\r\n\r\npublic class BadConfig implements ParallelExecutionConfigurationStrategy {\r\n\r\n    @Override\r\n    public ParallelExecutionConfiguration createConfiguration(ConfigurationParameters configurationParameters) {\r\n        return new ParallelExecutionConfiguration() {\r\n            @Override\r\n            public int getParallelism() {\r\n                return 1;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            @Override\r\n            public int getMinimumRunnable() {\r\n                return 1;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            @Override\r\n            public int getMaxPoolSize() {\r\n                return 0; // Invalid because < parallelism\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            @Override\r\n            public int getCorePoolSize() {\r\n                return 0;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            @Override\r\n            public int getKeepAliveSeconds() {\r\n                return 0;\r\n            }\r\n        };\r\n    }\r\n\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nWill cause the constructor of the `ForkJoinPool` to throw an `IllegalArgumentException`:\r\n\r\n```java\r\n        int p = parallelism;\r\n        if (p <= 0 || p > MAX_CAP || p > maximumPoolSize || keepAliveTime <= 0L)\r\n            throw new IllegalArgumentException();\r\n```            \r\n\r\nThat will in turn trigger the fallback for Java 8 because any an all exceptions are caught indiscriminately.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/junit-team/junit5/blob/517bfd56ad8ba8d22609b5055f4bb46a3d38c953/junit-platform-engine/src/main/java/org/junit/platform/engine/support/hierarchical/ForkJoinPoolHierarchicalTestExecutorService.java#L82-L96\r\n\r\n## Deliverables\r\n\r\nEither:\r\n- [x] Validate and report invalid values in the `ParallelExecutionConfiguration`.\r\n\r\nOr:\r\n- Be more discerning when using the fall back to Java 8. Perhaps using the multi-release jar feature.\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"marcphilipp","id":214207,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIxNDIwNw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/214207?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp","html_url":"https://github.com/marcphilipp","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcphilipp/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/junit-team/junit-framework/issues/3045/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/junit-team/junit-framework/issues/3045/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}